## Tables
You can create a table by separating columns with `|` and the header from the body with a row of dashes.

| Name  | Role      | Notes                       |
| :---- | :-------: | --------------------------: |
| Alice | Maintainer | Writes most of the **core** code |
| Bob   | Reviewer  | `reviews`                   |

 ---

(heading H2 @0..10
  "Tables")
(paragraph @10..115
  "You can create a table by separating columns with "
  (Code "|")
  " and the header from the body with a row of dashes.")
(table [Left, Center, Right] @116..330
  (head "Name" "Role" "Notes")
  (row "Alice" "Maintainer" "Writes most of the core code")
  (row "Bob" "Reviewer" "reviews"))
